      <h2 class="text-center">Choosing a Personal Injury Law Firm in Tampa</h2>
      <p>
        If you are seeking legal representation because you have been injured,
        physically or psychologically, as a result of the negligence of another
        person or entity, then you need to find a personal injury law firm that
        works for you. At the Romano Law Firm, we help our Tampa clients
        understand their rights and take the time to understand each individual
        case. While many personal injury law firms follow the same procedure
        with every case they handle, the Romano Law Firm truly takes the time to
        understand your unique situation. We have the heart (and time) of a
        small firm with the muscle of a big firm.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        If you or someone you know has been injured through the fault of
        another, do not delay to call the Romano Law Firm. Insurance companies
        don’t want you to know this: injury victims who are represented by an
        attorney get paid more for their injuries than victims who are not
        represented by an attorney. That’s why it’s important to be
        well-represented in your personal injury cases.
      </p>
